<!-- pages/discovery/discovery.wxml -->
<!-- Discovery_Page（推荐基金）
     Req 15（扫描与报告）、Req 16（历史/复盘/批量删/追问）。 -->

<scroll-view class="discovery-page" scroll-y enhanced>

  <!-- ── 扫描/历史切换 Tab ─────────────────────────── -->
  <view class="disc-tab-bar">
    <view
      class="disc-tab {{subView === 'scan' ? 'disc-tab--active' : ''}}"
      bindtap="onSwitchToScan"
    >新建扫描</view>
    <view
      class="disc-tab {{subView === 'history' ? 'disc-tab--active' : ''}}"
      bindtap="onSwitchToHistory"
    >历史记录</view>
  </view>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
       扫描子视图（subView === 'scan'）
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <view wx:if="{{subView === 'scan'}}">

    <!-- ── 配置区（Req 15.1）─────────────────────────────── -->
    <view class="card disc-section" wx:if="{{jobPhase === 'idle' || jobPhase === 'failed'}}">
      <view class="disc-section__title">扫描配置</view>

      <!-- 扫描模式 -->
      <view class="form-row">
        <text class="form-label">扫描模式</text>
        <picker mode="selector" range="{{scanModes}}" range-key="label"
                value="{{scanModeIndex}}" bindchange="onScanModeChange">
          <view class="form-picker">
            <text>{{scanModes[scanModeIndex].label}}</text>
            <text class="form-picker__arrow">›</text>
          </view>
        </picker>
      </view>

      <!-- 关注方向（≤3，Req 15.1 / 10.7）-->
      <view class="form-col">
        <text class="form-label">关注方向（最多 3 个）</text>

        <!-- 已选关注方向 tags -->
        <view class="focus-tags" wx:if="{{focusSectors.length > 0}}">
          <view
            class="focus-tag"
            wx:for="{{focusSectors}}"
            wx:key="*this"
          >
            <text class="focus-tag__label">{{item}}</text>
            <text class="focus-tag__remove" data-sector="{{item}}" bindtap="onRemoveFocusSector">×</text>
          </view>
        </view>
        <view wx:else class="disc-placeholder-text">暂未选择关注方向</view>

        <!-- 候选板块滚动选择（Req 15.2）-->
        <view class="sectors-picker" wx:if="{{sectorsAvailable.length > 0}}">
          <scroll-view scroll-x class="sectors-scroll">
            <view class="sectors-row">
              <view
                wx:for="{{sectorsAvailable}}"
                wx:key="sector_name"
                class="sector-chip {{focusSectors.indexOf(item.sector_name) !== -1 ? 'sector-chip--active' : ''}}"
                data-sector="{{item.sector_name || item}}"
                bindtap="onAddFocusSector"
              >
                <text>{{item.sector_name || item}}</text>
              </view>
            </view>
          </scroll-view>
        </view>
        <view wx:elif="{{sectorsLoading}}" class="disc-placeholder-text">加载板块中…</view>
      </view>

      <!-- 选基策略 -->
      <view class="form-row">
        <text class="form-label">选基策略</text>
        <picker mode="selector" range="{{strategyOptions}}" range-key="label"
                value="{{strategyIndex}}" bindchange="onStrategyChange">
          <view class="form-picker">
            <text>{{strategyOptions[strategyIndex].label}}</text>
            <text class="form-picker__arrow">›</text>
          </view>
        </picker>
      </view>

      <!-- 基金类型偏好 -->
      <view class="form-row">
        <text class="form-label">类型偏好</text>
        <picker mode="selector" range="{{fundTypeOptions}}" range-key="label"
                value="{{fundTypeIndex}}" bindchange="onFundTypeChange">
          <view class="form-picker">
            <text>{{fundTypeOptions[fundTypeIndex].label}}</text>
            <text class="form-picker__arrow">›</text>
          </view>
        </picker>
      </view>

      <!-- 预算 -->
      <view class="form-row">
        <text class="form-label">预算（元，选填）</text>
        <input
          class="form-input"
          type="digit"
          placeholder="如：10000"
          value="{{budgetYuan}}"
          bindinput="onBudgetInput"
        />
      </view>

      <!-- 分析模式 -->
      <view class="form-row">
        <text class="form-label">分析模式</text>
        <view class="segmented">
          <view
            wx:for="{{modeOptions}}"
            wx:key="value"
            class="segmented__item {{modeIndex === index ? 'segmented__item--active' : ''}}"
            data-value="{{index}}"
            bindtap="onModeChange"
          >{{item.label}}</view>
        </view>
      </view>

      <!-- AI 角色设定（Req 15.3）-->
      <view class="form-col">
        <view class="form-row form-row--between">
          <text class="form-label">AI 角色设定</text>
          <view class="btn btn-secondary btn--xs" bindtap="onSavePrompt">保存</view>
        </view>
        <textarea
          class="form-textarea"
          placeholder="输入荐基 AI 角色提示词（可选）…"
          value="{{systemRolePrompt}}"
          bindinput="onPromptInput"
          maxlength="500"
          auto-height
        />
      </view>
    </view>

    <!-- ── 开始扫描按钮（Req 15.4）────────────────────── -->
    <view class="disc-actions" wx:if="{{jobPhase === 'idle' || jobPhase === 'failed'}}">
      <view class="btn btn-primary btn--lg disc-actions__btn" bindtap="onStartScan">
        开始扫描
      </view>
    </view>

    <!-- ── 轮询进度（Req 15.5）──────────────────────────── -->
    <view class="card disc-section disc-progress"
          wx:if="{{jobPhase === 'submitting' || jobPhase === 'polling'}}">
      <view class="disc-progress__icon">⏳</view>
      <view class="disc-progress__stage">
        {{jobPhase === 'submitting' ? '正在提交任务…' : (jobStageLabel || '扫描中…')}}
      </view>
      <view class="disc-progress__hint">荐基扫描约需 30–120 秒，请稍候</view>
      <view class="disc-progress__bar">
        <view class="disc-progress__fill"></view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <!-- ── 失败态（Req 15.4 error path）───────────────── -->
    <view class="card disc-section disc-fail" wx:if="{{jobPhase === 'failed'}}">
      <view class="disc-fail__icon">✗</view>
      <text class="disc-fail__msg">{{jobError || '荐基扫描失败，请重试'}}</text>
      <view class="btn btn-secondary btn--sm" bindtap="onReScan">重新扫描</view>
    </view>

    <!-- ── 荐基报告（Req 15.6）──────────────────────────── -->
    <view class="card disc-section" wx:if="{{jobPhase === 'completed' && reportMarkdown}}">
      <view class="disc-section__title">荐基报告</view>
      <md-view markdown="{{reportMarkdown}}" />
    </view>

    <!-- ── 推荐基金列表（Req 15.6 + 15.7）─────────────── -->
    <view class="card disc-section"
          wx:if="{{jobPhase === 'completed' && discoveryReport && discoveryReport.recommended_funds && discoveryReport.recommended_funds.length > 0}}">
      <view class="disc-section__title">推荐基金</view>
      <view
        class="fund-item"
        wx:for="{{discoveryReport.recommended_funds}}"
        wx:key="fund_code"
        data-fund="{{item}}"
        bindtap="onFundPreviewTap"
      >
        <view class="fund-item__main">
          <text class="fund-item__name">{{item.fund_name || item.fund_code}}</text>
          <text class="fund-item__code">{{item.fund_code}}</text>
        </view>
        <view class="fund-item__meta" wx:if="{{item.reason}}">
          <text class="fund-item__reason">{{item.reason}}</text>
        </view>
        <text class="fund-item__arrow">›</text>
      </view>
    </view>

    <!-- ── 操作按钮行（完成后）──────────────────────────── -->
    <view class="disc-btn-row"
          wx:if="{{jobPhase === 'completed' && discoveryReport}}">
      <view class="btn btn-secondary btn--sm" bindtap="onToggleChat">
        {{showChat ? '收起追问' : 'AI 追问'}}
      </view>
      <view class="btn btn-secondary btn--sm" bindtap="onReScan">
        重新扫描
      </view>
    </view>

    <!-- ── AI 追问面板（Req 16.4–16.6，通过 chat-panel）── -->
    <view class="card disc-section disc-chat-section"
          wx:if="{{showChat && chatReportId}}">
      <view class="disc-section__title">AI 追问</view>
      <chat-panel
        reportId="{{chatReportId}}"
        chatType="discovery"
        loading="{{false}}"
      />
    </view>

  </view><!-- /scan subView -->

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
       历史子视图（subView === 'history'）Req 16.1–16.6
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <view wx:if="{{subView === 'history'}}">

    <!-- 顶部操作栏：多选 / 批量删除 -->
    <view class="disc-history-toolbar">
      <view
        class="btn btn-secondary btn--xs"
        bindtap="onToggleSelectMode"
      >{{isSelecting ? '取消' : '多选'}}</view>
      <view
        wx:if="{{isSelecting}}"
        class="btn btn-danger btn--xs"
        bindtap="onBatchDelete"
      >删除选中（{{selectedCount}}）</view>
    </view>

    <!-- 加载中 -->
    <view class="disc-placeholder-text" wx:if="{{historyLoading}}">加载中…</view>

    <!-- 错误态 -->
    <view class="card disc-section disc-fail" wx:elif="{{historyError}}">
      <view class="disc-fail__icon">⚠</view>
      <text class="disc-fail__msg">{{historyError}}</text>
      <view class="btn btn-secondary btn--sm" bindtap="onRetryHistory">重试</view>
    </view>

    <!-- 空态 -->
    <view class="disc-placeholder-text"
          wx:elif="{{!historyLoading && historyList.length === 0}}">
      暂无历史荐基报告
    </view>

    <!-- 历史报告列表（Req 16.1）-->
    <view class="card disc-section" wx:elif="{{historyList.length > 0}}">
      <view
        class="hist-item {{isSelecting && selectedIds[item.id] ? 'hist-item--selected' : ''}}"
        wx:for="{{historyList}}"
        wx:key="id"
        data-id="{{item.id}}"
        bindtap="onToggleSelectReport"
      >
        <!-- 多选复选框 -->
        <view class="hist-item__checkbox" wx:if="{{isSelecting}}">
          <view class="checkbox {{selectedIds[item.id] ? 'checkbox--checked' : ''}}">
            <text wx:if="{{selectedIds[item.id]}}" class="checkbox__tick">✓</text>
          </view>
        </view>

        <!-- 报告信息 -->
        <view class="hist-item__body">
          <view class="hist-item__title">
            {{item.scan_mode || item.title || '荐基报告'}}
          </view>
          <view class="hist-item__date" wx:if="{{item.created_at}}">
            {{item.created_at}}
          </view>
          <view class="hist-item__meta" wx:if="{{item.focus_sectors && item.focus_sectors.length > 0}}">
            <text
              class="hist-item__tag"
              wx:for="{{item.focus_sectors}}"
              wx:key="*this"
              wx:for-item="sector"
            >{{sector}}</text>
          </view>
        </view>

        <!-- 操作按钮（非多选模式）-->
        <view class="hist-item__actions" wx:if="{{!isSelecting}}">
          <view
            class="btn btn-secondary btn--xs"
            data-id="{{item.id}}"
            catchtap="onViewOutcomes"
          >复盘</view>
          <view
            class="btn btn-secondary btn--xs"
            data-id="{{item.id}}"
            catchtap="onOpenHistoryReport"
          >追问</view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>

  </view><!-- /history subView -->

  <!-- 底部留白 -->
  <view style="height: 40rpx;"></view>

</scroll-view>

<!-- ── 推荐基金详情预览弹层（Req 15.7）─────────────── -->
<view class="fund-preview-mask" wx:if="{{showFundPreview}}" bindtap="onCloseFundPreview">
  <view class="fund-preview-sheet" catchtap>
    <view class="fund-preview__header">
      <text class="fund-preview__title">{{previewFund.fund_name || previewFund.fund_code}}</text>
      <text class="fund-preview__code">代码：{{previewFund.fund_code}}</text>
    </view>

    <view class="fund-preview__body">
      <!-- 推荐理由 -->
      <view class="fund-preview__row" wx:if="{{previewFund.reason}}">
        <text class="fund-preview__row-label">推荐理由</text>
        <text class="fund-preview__row-value">{{previewFund.reason}}</text>
      </view>
      <!-- 建议仓位 / 比例 -->
      <view class="fund-preview__row" wx:if="{{previewFund.target_weight_percent != null}}">
        <text class="fund-preview__row-label">建议仓位</text>
        <num-text value="{{previewFund.target_weight_percent}}" kind="percent" />
      </view>
      <!-- 预期收益区间 -->
      <view class="fund-preview__row" wx:if="{{previewFund.expected_return_hint}}">
        <text class="fund-preview__row-label">预期收益参考</text>
        <text class="fund-preview__row-value">{{previewFund.expected_return_hint}}</text>
      </view>
      <!-- 风险提示 -->
      <view class="fund-preview__row" wx:if="{{previewFund.risk_note}}">
        <text class="fund-preview__row-label">风险提示</text>
        <text class="fund-preview__row-value disc-risk-text">{{previewFund.risk_note}}</text>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="fund-preview__footer">
      <view class="btn btn-primary btn--lg" bindtap="onGoToFundDetail">查看基金详情</view>
      <view class="btn btn-secondary btn--sm" bindtap="onCloseFundPreview">关闭</view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>

<!-- ── 复盘弹层（Req 16.3）─────────────────────────── -->
<view class="fund-preview-mask" wx:if="{{showOutcomes}}" bindtap="onCloseOutcomes">
  <view class="fund-preview-sheet" catchtap>
    <view class="fund-preview__header">
      <text class="fund-preview__title">荐基复盘</text>
    </view>

    <!-- 加载中 -->
    <view class="disc-placeholder-text" wx:if="{{outcomesLoading}}">加载复盘中…</view>

    <!-- 错误 -->
    <view wx:elif="{{outcomesError}}">
      <text class="disc-fail__msg">{{outcomesError}}</text>
    </view>

    <!-- 复盘数据 -->
    <view class="fund-preview__body" wx:elif="{{outcomesData}}">
      <!-- 整体收益 -->
      <view class="fund-preview__row" wx:if="{{outcomesData.overall_return_percent != null}}">
        <text class="fund-preview__row-label">整体收益</text>
        <num-text value="{{outcomesData.overall_return_percent}}" kind="percent" signed="{{true}}" />
      </view>
      <!-- 推荐基金复盘列表 -->
      <view wx:if="{{outcomesData.fund_outcomes && outcomesData.fund_outcomes.length > 0}}">
        <view class="disc-section__title" style="margin-bottom: 12rpx;">推荐基金表现</view>
        <view
          class="outcome-item"
          wx:for="{{outcomesData.fund_outcomes}}"
          wx:key="fund_code"
        >
          <view class="outcome-item__name">{{item.fund_name || item.fund_code}}</view>
          <view class="outcome-item__row">
            <text class="fund-preview__row-label">区间涨跌</text>
            <num-text
              wx:if="{{item.return_percent != null}}"
              value="{{item.return_percent}}"
              kind="percent"
              signed="{{true}}"
            />
            <text wx:else class="fund-preview__row-value">–</text>
          </view>
          <view class="outcome-item__row" wx:if="{{item.outcome_note}}">
            <text class="fund-preview__row-label">说明</text>
            <text class="fund-preview__row-value">{{item.outcome_note}}</text>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>
      <!-- 摘要文字 -->
      <view class="fund-preview__row" wx:if="{{outcomesData.summary}}">
        <text class="fund-preview__row-value" style="line-height:1.7;">{{outcomesData.summary}}</text>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="fund-preview__footer">
      <view class="btn btn-secondary btn--sm" bindtap="onCloseOutcomes">关闭</view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
